"Disables microphone and video access" = "Deaktivira pristup mikrofonu i videu";

"Disables orientation and motion data access" = "Deaktivira pristup podacima orijentacije i kretanja";

"Easy breezy. Though it could be dangerous." = "Propusno, ali može biti opasno.";

